TextView.android:text:
1.创建一个LiveData实例来保存数据
        \nMutableLiveData<String> currentName = new MutableLiveData<String>();
        \n
        \n2.创建Observer监听数据改变
        \nfinal Observer<String> nameObserver = new Observer<String>() {
            \n@Override\n
            public void onChanged(@Nullable final String newName) {\n
                //更新UI操作\n
                nameTextView.setText(newName);\n
            }\n
        };
        \n3.添加Observer
        \n        currentName.observe(this, nameObserver);
        \n4.设置值
        \n        currentName.setValue('xxxx');
